Name: Fire Bow
Notes: arrow lasts 30 frames minimum (if it doesnrt hit ground), 13 rames startup and 25 frames endlag upon release

Name: Boomerang
Notes: 20 frames to catch the boomerang.

Name: Bomb
Notes: bomb pulled out on frame 16. able to start throwing on frame 40. bomb has multipule hitboxes, unknown how much each does (damage listed assumes all hits land)

Name: Up Smash
Notes: 4 hits, first hit frames 11-14 and does 3% and 3 frames shield stun. second hit frames 26-28 and does 2% damage and 2 frames shield stun. third hit frames 40-42 can do 7 or 8% damage and 5 frames shield stun. last hit frames 43-44 and can do 8 or 9% damage and 5 or 6 frames shield stun

Name: Down Smash
Notes: front hit frames 9-11, does 13% or 7% damage. back hit frames 21-23, does 12% or 6% damage

Name: Neutral Air
Notes: weak hit frames 6-27

Name: Forward Air
Notes: first hit frames 14-16, does 12%, 11%, or 9% damage. Second hit frames 17-33, does 8%, 7%, or 5% damage with 5 frames shield stun

Name: Down Air
Notes: meteor hitbox frames 16-64

Name: Spin Attack
Notes: x amount of 1% hitboxes followed by 3% hitbox

Name: Rapid Jabs
Notes: rapid jab has an additional 7 frames of startup and 10 fames of endlag

Name: Spin Attack (Air)
Notes: x amount of 1% hitboxes followed by 3% hitbox

Name: Grab
Notes: Close grab is frame 11-13, hook is frame 11-14.

Name: Dashgrab
Notes: Close grab is frame 14-15, hook is frame 14-17.
